Text: RE Transportation Across SoCals System to Mexico Cc not have an international tariff rate If you have any questions please call Paul Borkovich at Original Message From Cherry Brian TPBKC Sent Friday October PM To Jeff Dasovich Cc Wong Mary S TPMSC Maralit Nena TPFXM Subject RE Transportation Across SoCals System to Mexico Please forward copies of our Mexico tariff to Jeff Original Message From Jeff Dasovich mailto Sent Friday October PM To Cherry Brian TPBKC Subject Transportation Across SoCals System to Mexico Brian Could you please forward me or direct me to SoCalGas tariffs describing the rates terms and conditions for moving gas over SoCals system into Mexico Thank you very much for your help Best Jeff atthtm
